{"tid":2218422,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平係點靠小學學歷砌低啲人做國家主席的?","createTime":"2020-09-26T07:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T13:56:31.000Z","uid":366884,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"96f254a6939cf86977d698b997ad18394890da9e","tid":2218422,"uid":366884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:51:20.000Z","msg":"認真好奇一問。睇佢上任以嚟嘅決策，同埋平時字都唔識多個，應該真係讀書少，但點解咁都上到位?係咪姐係佢係權鬥方面嘅天賦夠高，但其他方面係on9?<br />\n想問有冇ching知佢係點一步步爬上主席個位的?始終覺得小學生都做到國家主席好傳奇同荒謬。"},{"pid":"a308b9379563f6b44e09b31ac1942fc58129c6c8","tid":2218422,"uid":284630,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:57:18.000Z","msg":"佢假假地都係開國元老個仔<br />\n同埋好似開六合彩咁, 緊有人中頭獎"},{"pid":"4c7a2e5c9aebe60dbc32e6567f5f2a6c7af974ab","tid":2218422,"uid":20563,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T08:02:47.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過無能係一種優勢？<br />\n<br />\n胡撚塗同too simple too navie 以為揀個on9 既易控制咪俾佢上位。<br />\n<br />\n點知係on9 既盡頭係為左個位帶頭攬炒姐？"},{"pid":"c0acc9536a2b2281c7b11ebcfbf0db80d2f8c648","tid":2218422,"uid":226695,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T08:03:47.000Z","msg":"唔關學歷事 關背景事<br />\n<br />\n你要做主席前題係入中央政治局，中央政治局常委係中央最高權力嘅部門，入面全部都係名門望族，出身官二代，只有權鬥同識得玩弄政治先可以爭到上主席位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但上到去都唔可以掉以輕心，一不留神分分鐘俾人拉落馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸：有研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f0c5265aee9e34c5c67c916774e922457ba81f","tid":2218422,"uid":312114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T08:04:01.000Z","msg":"權鬥唔睇學歷"},{"pid":"a236c71ab1cc5176ba4fc03198f32f111ccaa14f","tid":2218422,"uid":261937,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T08:07:38.000Z","msg":"黑社會讀咁書做咩？"},{"pid":"d551f65686dadd26453c1e7d3d009d743a8f851b","tid":2218422,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T08:09:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7cfaa75ec1ea3354f9cce04ff886ee757208c4e8","tid":2218422,"uid":226695,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T08:09:40.000Z","msg":"習近平老豆習仲勳已經係老毛時代<br />\n習仲勳成功帶領廣洲行經濟起飛，驗證左鄧小平改革開放嘅成功，果陣已經為佢個仆街仔 入去中央政治局常委鋪路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d257645e24f0e1f9fc90aa7595e3e826fe07371","tid":2218422,"uid":242010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T08:19:19.000Z","msg":"識投胎"},{"pid":"b0a78b044995a7d65be9f8044e56404b7a45f72e","tid":2218422,"uid":23833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T08:37:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dba4140633f0e904272edc5240930969e974cb8e","tid":2218422,"uid":51121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T08:38:30.000Z","msg":"呢度啲人個個人中龍就做地底泥 習近平小學生就可以做國家主席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d65800eb3ec836c67ddf292a60ca42e69d1b8d7","tid":2218422,"uid":342929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T10:34:43.000Z","msg":"紅二代wo"},{"pid":"0aad42a8c5bc421fedcccf140309237d8fa1c9d0","tid":2218422,"uid":283908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T10:41:22.000Z","msg":"話係小學生 你就信佢係小學生?"},{"pid":"7466fc8b558af70cc5e000cd9871c985cdf4c070","tid":2218422,"uid":366884,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"0aad42a8c5bc421fedcccf140309237d8fa1c9d0","tid":2218422,"uid":283908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T10:41:22.000Z","msg":"話係小學生 你就信佢係小學生?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:19:39.000Z","msg":"字都未識讀，唔係小學生學歷都唔方高啦。。"},{"pid":"34afa39f0dd9097c8259ee93fb65cda78677deee","tid":2218422,"uid":56107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T13:50:52.000Z","msg":"讀到大學，讀埋博士就識權鬥？<img src